('16198', '817', 'Kaltoh Kurzon', 'Brother to Zerim Kurzon himself, the founder of the Kurzon mercenary network, Kaltoh is very experienced in the field of bounty hunting. He has reportedly been working for various factions throughout the galaxy of late, as an independent mercenary. Threat level: Deadly', '', '10900000', '109000', '235', '1', '2', '0', '0'),
