('17645', '494', 'Deadspace Control Station', 'Bases such as this one are commonly used as on-site mining posts or colonies. They are often obscurely located and vulnerable as well and therefore it is common that pirates make their homes in them, sometimes with the resident''s full consent. This one looks unusually exposed and vulnerable due to what appear to be major renovations.', '', '0', '1', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0'),
