('17857', '476', 'Mjolnir Citadel Torpedo', 'Citadel Torpedoes are behemoths designed for maximum firepower against capital ships and installations. They are usable only by capital ships and starbase defense batteries.\r\n\r\nNothing more than a baby nuclear warhead, this guided missile wreaks havoc with the delicate electronic systems aboard a starship. Specifically designed to damage shield systems, it is able to ravage heavily shielded targets in no time.', '21_14', '1500', '0.3', '0', '100', '0', '350000', '1193'),
