('17859', '476', 'Scourge Citadel Torpedo', 'Citadel Torpedoes are behemoths designed for maximum firepower against capital ships and installations. They are usable only by capital ships and starbase defense batteries.\r\n\r\nFitted with a graviton pulse generator, this weapon causes massive damage as it overwhelms ships'' internal structures, tearing bulkheads and armor plating apart with frightening ease.', '21_02', '1500', '0.3', '0', '100', '0', '300000', '1193'),
