('19982', '86', 'Sanshas Infrared S', 'Modulates the beam of a laser weapon into the infrared frequencies. Slightly improved range. Slightly increased EM damage.\r\n\r\nThe delicate crystalline structures used in the manufacture of this advanced crystal degrade with use, eventually causing it to shatter.\r\n\r\n20% increased optimal range.\r\n35% reduced capacitor need.', '08_07', '1', '1', '0', '1', '0', '4000', '997'),
